Package: xeniumPanelExplorer
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Browser and Reclusterer for Xenium Prime 5K Subpanels
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Smith", "JT", email = "smith6jt@ufl.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Shiny app for exploring 49 curated subpanels of the 10x Genomics
    Xenium Prime 5K Human Pan Tissue and Pathways panel and re-clustering
    user-loaded Xenium runs against any chosen subpanel.
